Step 1: Open "server.py" and import the necessary modules 
Step 2: Then change the recipient email and sender email and also change the app password for the sender email
Step 3: Enter the website link which you have to check
Step 4: Then run the code and wait for the result message in your console, if the server is up then the message will appear as "Server is UP" in the console or 
        if the server is down then an email will be sent to the recipient with an error message
Step 4: And if you want to check the timeframe and status of your execution then open "status.py" and run the code to see the status
